name: Bhimavarapu Koushik Reddy
about: I am Bhimavarapu Koushik Reddy, currently pursuing a degree in Computer Science and Information Technology with a specialization in Cybersecurity at Koneru Lakshmaiah Education Foundation, set to graduate in 2026. As a tech enthusiast, I possess strong programming skills and thrive in collaborative team environments. Known for my adaptability and effective communication, I am keen on excelling in the dynamic field of cybersecurity. My interest lies in developing robust security solutions, and I am dedicated to staying updated on the latest trends and technologies. I am open to networking, collaborations, and discussions related to cybersecurity and technology.

experiences.title: Head of Technological Council - KL SAC
experiences.description: As a core member of the Technological Council, I play a pivotal role in driving technological initiatives and projects within the organization. I collaborate with fellow council members to develop and implement strategies aimed at enhancing our technological infrastructure and capabilities. My responsibilities include overseeing project management, facilitating workshops and seminars, and ensuring the alignment of technology projects with the organization's goals. Through my contributions, I help foster a culture of innovation and continuous improvement, ultimately contributing to the organization's success and growth.

experiences.title: Administrative Secretary
experiences.description: KL Empower is a college club dedicated to creating a safe, non-judgmental space for victims of abuse. We raise awareness about consent, combat stigma around abuse, and support survivors through emotional aid and resources like therapy and legal assistance. Our initiatives include awareness campaigns and educational workshops aimed at prevention and support.
